The course discusses the possibilities of applying digital tools and various online solutions to enrich the learning of Estonian as a second language and to develop the digital competence of learners.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course discusses the possibilities of applying digital tools and various online solutions to enrich the learning of Estonian as a second language and to develop the digital competence of learners.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  A student who has successfully completed the course - knows the components of digital competence and the learner's digital competence model; - knows the basics of creating digital learning material; - analyzes Estonian language learning materials from the point of view of the possibilities of enriching them with digital learning materials; - prepares Estonian language learning activities that develop learners' digital competence; - prepares digital learning materials, including online game-based learning activities.
